   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00101"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">XVIII Spöttelgasse 7</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00102"/>Liebenswürdiger!</salute></opener><p>wir nehmen an, Sie wollen Ihr <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29985" subtype="implied">Manu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cript</rs> in <hi rend="underline" n="2">Ihrer</hi> Wohnung <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01336-1"/><date><hi rend="latintype">Donnerstag</hi></date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01336-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="See" target="1903-11-12"/>.
               </note> vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. Nun gut: dann aber bitte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>päte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens <time>½ 6</time> anfangen.
               Andernfalls ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teht die ekelhafte Gehetztheit. Wir werden also um <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01336-2"/><time>5 ¼</time><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01336-2">17 Uhr 15</note>
               anklopfen.</p><closer><signed>Hugo</signed></closer><postscript><p rend="right">(auch für <rs ref="#pmb10863" type="person">Richard</rs>)</p><p><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>6 XI.</date></p></postscript></div>
      </body>
